          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "If your descendants obey the terms of my covenant and the laws that I teach them, then your royal line will continue forever and ever.” "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "If your descendants obey the terms of my covenant and the laws that I teach them, then your royal line will continue forever and ever.”"
